ed contract; verify machine identity preservation end-to-end. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-020** [T1] Integrate partitura for phrase-feature extraction: harmonic_charge, melodic_charge, metric_weight, cadential detection, contour apex. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-021** [T1] Implement R9 Motif Memory: LRU cache of motif hashes with variation menu and return-home decay. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-022** [T1] Implement R10 Silence Budget: per-voice and per-section accumulators enforced at phrase boundaries. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-023** [T1] Implement wind/voice lung-capacity constraints: 4–8 s continuous-play cap per instrument-sim voice. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-024** [T1] Implement R11 Call-Response Gating: follower phrase intent complements leader's realized performance. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-025** [T1] Compose SectionEnvelope with phrase arcs multiplicatively so section-level tempo elasticity modulates phrase-level shaping. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-026** [T1] Implement tempo-dependent swing curve per Friberg/Sundström (3.5:1 at slow tempi down toward 1:1 at fast), with short-note near-constant ~100 ms. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-027** [T1] Add arc-shape variety so not every phrase uses a symmetric parabola: per-phrase random selection from parabolic/cosine/asymmetric-Bezier/flat/inverted with peak-position variance. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-028** [T1] Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-014** [T2] Add systemd unit `cypherclaw-sample-capture.service` that runs `sample_capture_daemon.py` with `Restart=always`, dependent on `cypherclaw-jack.service`. (~6h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\