ension, breath insertion, and budget accounting |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| 9 | T-009 | Implement R7 Articulation Shaping: per-note gate-time by style (legato 0.95–1.02, normal 0.7–0.85, staccato 0.3–0.5, staccatissimo 0.15–0.25) with contour adjustments. | T1 | 5 | 3 | CCH-018 | — | - `render/rules/articulation.py` sets dur_sec as gate_time × nominal<br/>- repeated-pitch notes slightly shorter (×0.92); notes after upward leaps slightly longer (×1.05)<br/>- tests verify gate-time range per style and contour adjustments |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-| 10 | T-010 | Implement R8 Microtiming Polish: per-note Gaussian jitter σ=3 ms on melodic, 1 ms on ostinato, 0 ms on grid-locked machine voices. | T1 | 4 | 3 | CCH-019 | — | - `render/rules/microtiming.py` is the ONLY place white noise enters the pipeline<br/>- σ values below listener JND (10 ms) by design<br/>- grid-locked voices receive σ=0 and emerge with timing_deviation_ms==0<br/>- tests verify σ by role and zero-jitter on grid-locked |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 1 | T-001 | Implement buffer-management protocol: `OnSamplerLoad(record)` allocates scsynth buffer + reads WAV; `OnSamplerFree` releases buffer; LRU eviction at 64-buffer cap. | T1 | 4 | 3 | CCS-010 | — | - `tools/senseweave/sampler_buffers.py` exposes `BufferPool(scsynth_client, capacity=64)` with `acquire(record) -> bufnum`, `release(record)`, `evict_lru()`<br/>- WAV file path → `/b_allocRead bufnum path 0 -1` over OSC<br/>- LRU eviction triggered automatically when `acquire` exceeds capacity<br/>- on scsynth restart, pool detects buffer-id reuse failure and rebuilds<br/>- tests with a mock OSC client verify allocate, evict, release, and reuse paths |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 2 | T-002 | Implement `sampler_effects.scd` dedicated effects-bus SynthDef chain: long delay (1/4 to 1/2 measure), convolution reverb (FreeVerb fallback if no IR loaded), spectral freeze (PV_Freeze), comb-resonance tuned to B fundamental (61.74 Hz). | 