    25	
    26	Systemd `--user` units (e.g. `cypherclaw-narrative-api.service`) only survive
    27	after the operator's interactive session ends if **linger** is enabled for that
    28	account. Without linger, the user systemd manager is torn down on SSH logout
    29	and the service stops with it, defeating CN-013 / CN-015 (service must restart
    30	automatically across reboot and remain active without an attached session).
